Thank you so much for being my model at @pmtslv today @karatiana_ 🫶🏻🫶🏻🫶🏻 it’s always so fun getting to teach for future professionals! @chitabeseau and I had a great first class together and the best crowd of students ☺️

#shaghaircut #shag #curtainbangs #lasvegashair #lasvegashairstylist #vegashairstylist

VEGAS STYLISTS! Mark your calendars for an afternoon of color correcting and shag cutting with me and @chitabeseau at @hotboxsalon 💜 link to tickets in bio! 
We will also be hitting the road with this class, so if you’d like to host us at your salon, let us know 🫶🏻

Thank you for our flyer @gmsanchez 💚

@thedarkestdark inspired me to dye my hair pink 💕 love you so much friend and truly appreciate you trusting me with your first real cut in years!

#shaghaircut #curtainbangs #lasvegashairstylist #lasvegashairstylists #hendersonhairstylist #sharkfinshears #hotboxsalon

@chitabeseau and I had such a good time teaching at @pmtslv 💕 come see us in action on August 14 from 1-3 pm at @hotboxsalon teaching color correction and shag haircutting! One lucky person will win a free pair of scissors from @sharkfinshears at our class! Link to tickets in bio 🫶🏻 
🎥: @gmsanchez

My first baby wanted some blue in his hair! This kid hasn’t let me do his hair in years cause he straight up told me I don’t know how to do stylish hair (please tell him I’m cool y’all) 
This was a new core memory for me and I’m so glad I got to share this with experience with him 🥹
His song choice cause it’s his new fave 🫶🏻

Cute lil purple peekaboos for Carolina 💜 
Colored with @oligopro styled with @verbproducts @dysonhair 🤍

3️⃣4️⃣ so grateful for my family, friends and career! Teenage Alex would be so proud of this woman and think she’s so cool and hot so that’s a win in my book 👏🏼

styled with @dysonhair and @hairstorystudio powder #moty2023

MINDFUL METHODS AT @hotboxsalon 💕 @chitabeseau

Color corrections are a process and a commitment! Consistent appointments, proper at home care, an open mind and realistic goals are all necessary 🫶🏻 
Our goal here was to keep her hair healthy and go back to her natural color after years of black box dye. Swipe for our starting point back in June! Thank you for being so patient and kind during this process @gothcharlotte 🤍
Big chop for @hllaspdrs 🩷💇🏻‍♀️ love how this shape refreshed the color placement and how dang good she looks with short hair!! Thank you for the trust 🫶🏻

Some goodies from 2023! Incredibly grateful for all of my clients. Thank you to everyone that sat in my chair this year and trusted me with their hair. I love you all! Here’s to another year of great hair 💇🏻‍♀️
